  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个完整的用户认证流程图，场景是已登录用户访问某个页面时的后台交互。核心要体现从UI到NGINX，再到RESTful API，最后落到Users微服务的完整链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Authenticated User",
        "UI",
        "NGINX",
        "RESTful API",
        "Users microservice"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这个流程里NGINX是只做反向代理，还是会涉及一些路径转换？比如用户访问的URL和实际后端服务的URL是不是不一样？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
        "RESTful API",
        "domain",
        "BEDomain"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这里有个关键转换。用户访问的是https://www.domain.com/api/something，但NGINX会把它代理到http://www.BEDomain.com/something，协议和域名都变了，路径里的/api前缀也要去掉。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
        "RESTful API",
        "domain",
        "BEDomain",
        "/api/something"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那RESTful API这边怎么处理认证？是直接自己验，还是再往下游调用？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RESTful API",
        "Authentication Middleware"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "RESTful API内部先过一层Authentication Middleware，然后发RPC到Users微服务做真正的Token校验。Users微服务要从Redis里取存储的Token做比对。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RESTful API",
        "Authentication Middleware",
        "Users microservice",
        "Users Redis",
        "token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我画一下：Users微服务调用Redis获取token，Redis返回后，微服务自己校验正确性，然后把结果返回给RESTful API。这里校验通过之后，RESTful API继续执行后续业务逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Users microservice",
        "Users Redis",
        "token",
        "RESTful API",
        "execution"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Users微服务返回给RESTful API的应该是校验结果吧？你刚才说的是\"返回存储的token\"，但实际应该是返回认证成功或失败的状态，或者重新签发的东西？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Users microservice",
        "RESTful API",
        "token",
        "returns"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "你说得对，我调整一下。Users微服务完成校验后，把认证结果返回给RESTful API。然后RESTful API继续执行剩余逻辑，最后把响应逐层返回：RESTful API → NGINX → UI → 最终用户，用户看到预期的页面动作执行完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Users microservice",
        "RESTful API",
        "NGINX",
        "UI",
        "Authenticated User",
        "response"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，整个链路闭环了。最后一步UI执行用户预期的动作，这样从用户视角看就是一次正常的页面访问。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UI",
        "Authenticated User",
        "expected action"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
